org.upmc.electisim

Class ElectionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.upmc.electisim.ElectionResult

  • public class ElectionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing the result of an election, containing the score map and the elected committee. Such objects are in general produced by the voting rules, implementing the interface IVotingRule.
